{"tid":2117461,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"白色恐怖觸發 港人憎恨政權","createTime":"2020-07-21T01:08:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T06:08:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eefd198eca9115f40d914c40f819981fe4201088","tid":2117461,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T01:08:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200721/ZMP3FSPWMNYOFK3ZR4ATCDA6O4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200721%2FZMP3FSPWMNYOFK3ZR4ATCDA6O4%2F&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhP8IAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=77fca47b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200721%2FZMP3FSPWMNYOFK3ZR4ATCDA6O4%2F&h=a8264f7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200721/ZMP3FSPWMNYOFK3ZR4ATCDA6O4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n白色恐怖觸發 港人憎恨政權<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/gOxY2d98o0_HRNKM6BXHtiukCwU=/1280x720/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EML2N2Z444M3WKMTGLNPNNOC3I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgOxY2d98o0_HRNKM6BXHtiukCwU%3D%2F1280x720%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEML2N2Z444M3WKMTGLNPNNOC3I.jpg&h=25265e26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n7.21襲擊是過去一年港人憎恨政權的最重要事件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【7.21周年】<br />\n<br />\n7.21襲擊的恐怖畫面及黑白分明的本質，成為不少人關注逆權運動的起點，但政權卻自製「官方真相」，企圖模糊事件。記者以問卷調查，了解一年後元朗民主派支持者對7.21襲擊看法。結果顯示，受訪者幾近一面倒否定政權和鄉紳對事件的論述，結果亦反映，7.21襲擊是過去一年港人憎恨政權的最重要事件。記者在初選首日，到元朗市中心兩個票站外進行問卷調查，共有212名支持民主派的元朗街坊接受訪問。<br />\n<br />\n7.21後，何君堯和當地鄉紳以事前得悉有人要入元朗「搞事」，需要「保家衞族」為由，企圖合理化襲擊途人行為。<br />\n<br />\n而警方則多番表示，由於當晚中聯辦和上環有激烈示威，警力被攤薄，為遲到39分鐘抵達西鐵站解畫。調查顯示，元朗人明顯不相信以上論述，約86%人不認同白衣人為「保家衞族」而作出攻擊，認同的僅有8.5%。超過99%人不認同警方當晚沒多餘人手應付事件。<br />\n<br />\n盧偉聰和鄧炳強兩。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n99.5%受訪者認為警縱容發生<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：避白衣人跌傷 坐輪椅常大哭  婆婆身心受創 斥政府漂白<br />\n<br />\n但這些說法無法在元朗人心中洗白，受訪者一面倒地（99.5%）認同7.21襲擊是在警方默許下發生，同時又有高達95%人認為政府高層或中央事前已得悉當日會發生襲擊。白衣暴徒拉起鐵閘，衝入西鐵站襲擊無辜途人震驚全港，亦成為不少人抗爭起點，逾37%人「非常認同」7.21是其關注抗爭運動的觸發點，表示「認同」的亦有30%。<br />\n<br />\n港區國安法規定，非法引起港人對中央或港府憎恨或犯法，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。高達37.7%選擇7.21事件，其次是警方圍攻中大、理大和政府堅拒成立獨立調查委員會。<br />\n<br />\n■記者關冠麒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/F3GqecVQsx1C3y2CNeMVVhESGJU=/1077x655/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BBI65XBXZLNP5TNWQQKKSFFUKE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FF3GqecVQsx1C3y2CNeMVVhESGJU%3D%2F1077x655%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBBI65XBXZLNP5TNWQQKKSFFUKE.gif&h=857cd941&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VCN5FzMqA128xeoUfdlDLPtT4Kg=/1139x658/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2VNXD6DZEDMZHXU5YJXH4KFQTU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVCN5FzMqA128xeoUfdlDLPtT4Kg%3D%2F1139x658%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2VNXD6DZEDMZHXU5YJXH4KFQTU.gif&h=120b891c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WzMDSnHwdtiuEtZFNeiwNV2Y8p8=/1077x689/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TBWNINC42J3PVMGYUFJ23TOEA4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWzMDSnHwdtiuEtZFNeiwNV2Y8p8%3D%2F1077x689%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTBWNINC42J3PVMGYUFJ23TOEA4.gif&h=0a803911&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f097e1e16537df37e4afcbe446e210b2f292a07","tid":2117461,"uid":237838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:08:3